46a109be-c847-4db3-b154-54156bce0e18.title: <player>
46a109be-c847-4db3-b154-54156bce0e18.text: Your animals don't look too healthy.

af1a72ce-b6d9-43cc-ac37-f6125dcd3f1d.title: Alice's husband
af1a72ce-b6d9-43cc-ac37-f6125dcd3f1d.text:
It's that fountain thingy in the temple to the east. It's
turned them all into zombies.

2cf82bb2-0fcc-4ca2-8ab4-b4c290ea1343.title: Alice's husband
2cf82bb2-0fcc-4ca2-8ab4-b4c290ea1343.text:
None at all, mate, except that those worshippers at that
temple keep comin' and killin' 'em all for their bones.
Don't ask me why.

45c96d9a-f4fe-44ed-98d4-aad3a7598749.title: <player>
45c96d9a-f4fe-44ed-98d4-aad3a7598749.text:
But you're a ghost - surely you know
something about it.

05290465-5b0d-402d-bfa5-8b6ccb8b024f.title: Alice's husband
05290465-5b0d-402d-bfa5-8b6ccb8b024f.text:
I don't know nuthin' about nuthin'. Oim a simple ghost
with simple needs. All I know is, years ago, that temple
started glowing green and, a few months later, I woke
up dead. That's all there is to it.

235a5b66-f3b1-4fb8-bb45-27e4ebc5a1b5.title: <player>
235a5b66-f3b1-4fb8-bb45-27e4ebc5a1b5.text: Your animals don't look too healthy.

e44b13ee-6b35-4792-b1a9-5172d792668b.title: Alice's husband
e44b13ee-6b35-4792-b1a9-5172d792668b.text:
It's that fountain thingy in the temple to the east. It's
turned them all into zombies.

90c6d76c-3a4d-405b-b5de-eace31722674.title: Alice's husband
90c6d76c-3a4d-405b-b5de-eace31722674.text:
None at all, mate, except that those worshippers at that
temple keep comin' and killin' 'em all for their bones.
Don't ask me why.

4576bd1e-3f77-471e-8d61-41b2e3a84729.title: <player>
4576bd1e-3f77-471e-8d61-41b2e3a84729.text:
But you're a ghost - surely you know
something about it.

ccb3c71d-ecf8-4fd6-bd98-a56043ed37ca.title: Alice's husband
ccb3c71d-ecf8-4fd6-bd98-a56043ed37ca.text:
I don't know nuthin' about nuthin'. Oim a simple ghost
with simple needs. All I know is, years ago, that temple
started glowing green and, a few months later, I woke
up dead. That's all there is to it.

24aaacb6-56d4-4ff3-9b4e-21f701addbf5.title: Alice's husband
24aaacb6-56d4-4ff3-9b4e-21f701addbf5.text: I do miss the wife though; tell 'er I still loves her.

ff54464b-c836-4bbd-a199-40b2f841908d.title: <player>
ff54464b-c836-4bbd-a199-40b2f841908d.text: Would I be able to buy some of your chickens?

958c4236-04d4-460d-900c-e874f4041ea5.title: Alice's husband
958c4236-04d4-460d-900c-e874f4041ea5.text: Talk to my wife and I'll think about it.

76794980-f898-43c9-b4b3-84ad025f6175.title: <player>
76794980-f898-43c9-b4b3-84ad025f6175.text:
Not yet; I've been distracted by the thought of undead
cow milk.

5d5280a5-8786-4ed9-bb82-f5bf9b1cfb20.title: Alice's husband
5d5280a5-8786-4ed9-bb82-f5bf9b1cfb20.text: 'Ave you talked to the wife for me?

7cd66ae6-cfc4-4b33-bd43-dcd148c1d45b.title: <player>
7cd66ae6-cfc4-4b33-bd43-dcd148c1d45b.text:
Your wife says she needs the family cash and wants to
know what you did with it.

4e717ace-2e61-45be-af1f-d06c8722247e.title: Alice's husband
4e717ace-2e61-45be-af1f-d06c8722247e.text: Tell 'er I spent it on cheap spirits, har har.

0b96f20f-aaa6-4c8d-a91a-569a7d300063.title: <player>
0b96f20f-aaa6-4c8d-a91a-569a7d300063.text: Your sense of humour died too, it seems...

200446d5-47ae-40cf-9ca4-10efa4d01a29.title: Alice's husband
200446d5-47ae-40cf-9ca4-10efa4d01a29.text: Hah, just trying to lift your spirits.

804fc427-3940-4339-84ef-2a21caeca379.title: Alice's husband
804fc427-3940-4339-84ef-2a21caeca379.text:
Suit yerself, stick-in-the-mud. Anyway, Oim not one o'
them yokels. Tell 'er I putted the cash in the bank like
she always told me to.

bf9683e4-78b7-4b5f-bf8e-97cfceb04824.title: Alice's husband
bf9683e4-78b7-4b5f-bf8e-97cfceb04824.text:
A warning to ya, too: annoy her and I'll haunt ya til
yer hair turns white.

c30d9d30-8264-42dc-94e3-6a92afd5ff6a.title: <player>
c30d9d30-8264-42dc-94e3-6a92afd5ff6a.text:
You may not believe me, but she wants me to find
your bank pass now.

762ca844-ae9b-4245-b88d-431efa7c7265.title: Alice's husband
762ca844-ae9b-4245-b88d-431efa7c7265.text:
Maybe she said that, maybe she didn't. I think you're
just after me savings. Tell 'er that no one but a fool
gives away their pass numbers.

48f34b3c-116a-4d0b-a1f3-c760c39d93f5.title: Alice's husband
48f34b3c-116a-4d0b-a1f3-c760c39d93f5.text:
Go tell 'er now, if you're not a double-dealin' scammer,
that is.

7b9c1575-f51e-4453-96aa-86086de11aba.title: <player>
7b9c1575-f51e-4453-96aa-86086de11aba.text:
I talked to your wife and thought that if you had a
special amulet, you could speak to her and sort out the
bank situation without me being involved.

a8ce8331-a117-49c1-a449-9a95b125f6c4.title: Alice's husband
a8ce8331-a117-49c1-a449-9a95b125f6c4.text:
Arr, that makes far more sense than I was expecting
from a muscle-head like you. My wife's a clever one.

627b521f-c61e-4721-8b41-6f3fd441c2a3.title: <player>
627b521f-c61e-4721-8b41-6f3fd441c2a3.text:
Well...oh, never mind. I'm working on getting the
amulet anyway.

27a8f298-49da-408e-ba99-75ef2e3bb10a.title: <player>
27a8f298-49da-408e-ba99-75ef2e3bb10a.text:
Well... oh, never mind. I'm desperate enough for those
chickens to let that pass.

3cc9a4a7-28c7-4284-990b-8da8be8c204a.title: Alice's husband
3cc9a4a7-28c7-4284-990b-8da8be8c204a.text:
Give me that amulet, then, and we'll be seeing about
your unnatural desire for chickens.

options.text: Okay, you need it more than I do, I suppose.
I don't think I'm ready to hand it over yet.

1d987b98-7a4a-45bf-9681-b82e11f3d1b5.title: <player>
1d987b98-7a4a-45bf-9681-b82e11f3d1b5.text: I don't think I'm ready to hand it over yet.

bddc4f0d-1a20-4d34-a3aa-b071145ab0fa.title: <player>
bddc4f0d-1a20-4d34-a3aa-b071145ab0fa.text: Okay, you need it more than I do, I suppose.

c36182bf-88a0-4459-a8fb-1ed965a82df0.title: <player>
c36182bf-88a0-4459-a8fb-1ed965a82df0.text: Lucky we had such a brilliant idea.

9a62b16c-3506-4503-952a-f532ea8f844f.title: Alice's husband
9a62b16c-3506-4503-952a-f532ea8f844f.text:
Ahhh, many thanks. Now what was it you were wanting
again?

c316ed88-2143-49ee-bb35-6d28b614fa51.title: <player>
c316ed88-2143-49ee-bb35-6d28b614fa51.text: I need a couple of your chickens.

cbcd0299-c672-4faa-97c7-2343c71ebc7c.title: Alice's husband
cbcd0299-c672-4faa-97c7-2343c71ebc7c.text:
Chickens is tricksy, 'specially dead 'uns. I'll have to catch
'em for ye.

cff92771-14a9-47d4-8686-43ff8af97e2f.title: <player>
cff92771-14a9-47d4-8686-43ff8af97e2f.text: They look pretty pathetic; how hard can it be?

117f2915-a425-48c2-a6fa-11d6fbda2eb6.title: Alice's husband
117f2915-a425-48c2-a6fa-11d6fbda2eb6.text: Stand back while I catches 'em, ya city slicker.

b26ddc4a-6a67-4feb-abe4-024474026454.title: Alice
b26ddc4a-6a67-4feb-abe4-024474026454.text: You heard my husband: leave now!

dd354cff-8338-4737-a9ee-ff794a88be55.title: Cow31337Killer
dd354cff-8338-4737-a9ee-ff794a88be55.text:
Always the same; I can never get these animals to
myself.

2623cbca-8993-446e-82b5-1920fc80a2fe.title: Cow31337Killer
2623cbca-8993-446e-82b5-1920fc80a2fe.text:
Buying cowhides and feathers - ahh, that chicken is
next; feathers for me!

d71f4ca7-3394-4644-98e5-7405cd8553f9.title: <player>
d71f4ca7-3394-4644-98e5-7405cd8553f9.text: Well, that's one way to catch a chicken, I suppose.

8ab822da-8115-4f1b-9101-cf30c530ead9.title: Alice's husband
8ab822da-8115-4f1b-9101-cf30c530ead9.text:
Hello, how can I help you? I'm sellin' if you have ecto-
tokens.

options.text: Could I buy those chickens now, then?
Your animals don't look too healthy.
Where can I get these ecto-tokens?

e23dbd50-ae84-417b-91b4-d66eee1b1666.title: Alice's husband
e23dbd50-ae84-417b-91b4-d66eee1b1666.text:
I can hand over a chicken if you give me 10 of them
ecto-token thingies per bird.

options.text: Your animals don't look too healthy; I'll buy elsewhere.

80889e6f-2341-4b0b-a70b-1046ca90fb41.title: <player>
80889e6f-2341-4b0b-a70b-1046ca90fb41.text: Could I buy those chickens now?

cffcd446-ccd3-4315-a3ae-489879ad6620.title: Alice's husband
cffcd446-ccd3-4315-a3ae-489879ad6620.text:
I'm not a charity here, ya know. Bad enough all you
cow-killing folks are a'slaughterin' me beasts. Come back
when ya have enough tokens.

341efe41-f72d-463d-b465-fbacd83bbb1e.title: Alice's husband
341efe41-f72d-463d-b465-fbacd83bbb1e.text:
Ta, some day soon I'll be havin' a nice undead bed to
kip in.

75109f34-b453-44b8-ab55-f738228822c5.title: <player>
75109f34-b453-44b8-ab55-f738228822c5.text: Your animals don't look too healthy; I'll buy elsewhere.

93679d7c-50e1-4195-b26c-7d2e08f6c5c6.title: Alice's husband
93679d7c-50e1-4195-b26c-7d2e08f6c5c6.text:
Har har, how many ghost chicky farmers d'you know,
den?

69ee8b5a-95a4-4bda-ba42-7bc5a32b218e.title: <player>
69ee8b5a-95a4-4bda-ba42-7bc5a32b218e.text: Your animals don't look too healthy.

cec71f48-501a-435c-a768-00fef7952b08.title: Alice's husband
cec71f48-501a-435c-a768-00fef7952b08.text:
It's that fountain thingy in the temple to the east. It's
turned them all into zombies.

d7885bc1-e5b3-4a99-b3c3-5ec65d05fea0.title: Alice's husband
d7885bc1-e5b3-4a99-b3c3-5ec65d05fea0.text:
None at all, mate, except that those worshippers at that
temple keep comin' and killin' 'em all for their bones.
Don't ask me why.

8f7ab19d-4ef4-438b-b308-db7ac7e74ec3.title: <player>
8f7ab19d-4ef4-438b-b308-db7ac7e74ec3.text:
But you're a ghost - surely you know
something about it.

24ec4ee6-4894-4766-ac4a-5bb197695f28.title: Alice's husband
24ec4ee6-4894-4766-ac4a-5bb197695f28.text:
I don't know nuthin' about nuthin'. Oim a simple ghost
with simple needs. All I know is, years ago, that temple
started glowing green and, a few months later, I woke
up dead. That's all there is to it.

f21e0761-aa65-4bf3-bf60-03ef8229c847.title: Alice's husband
f21e0761-aa65-4bf3-bf60-03ef8229c847.text:
The ghosts I talk to say that the tokens have something
to do with the tower just east of here. If you need to
collect some I'd try there.
